quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,When the earth is shaken by its earthquake
  99,2,and the earth unloads its heavy loads
  99,3,"and the human being says: what is the matter with it"
  99,4,On that day it speaks out its stories
  99,5,because your Master revealed to it
  99,6,On that day people come out in separate groups to be shown their works
  99,7,And anyone who does a tiny bit of good sees it
  99,8,and anyone who does a tiny bit of bad sees it